21
00:02:59,350 --> 00:03:00,150
That's her.

22
00:03:01,990 --> 00:03:02,790
Grand Elder,

23
00:03:03,220 --> 00:03:04,400
why can't we take

24
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:05,630
