A bit cold.

40
00:04:08,550 --> 00:04:09,790
Are you feeling any better?

41
00:04:14,580 --> 00:04:16,149
They are torturing you.

42
00:04:17,660 --> 00:04:19,060
It's spirit refinement.

43
00:04:19,310 --> 00:04:20,790
The spirit refinement is fake.

44
00:04:21,589 --> 00:04:22,550
You don't understand.

45
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:48,390
He's back!

46
00:04:54,470 --> 00:04:55,500
He's not doing well.

47
00:04:56,490 --> 00:04:57,380
Leave him to me.

48
00:05:05,630 --> 00:05:07,270
Tanyin, Tanyin.

49
00:05:07,670 --> 00:05:08,950
Return to the Divine Realm quickly to meet me.

50
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:25,270
Why have you summoned me?

51
00:05:25,270 --> 00:05:26,780
The Five Direction Deities of

52
00:05:26,950 --> 00:05:28,910
