587
00:28:36,340 --> 00:28:37,750
I still feel a bit risky.

588
00:28:41,570 --> 00:28:42,290
Where's Ji Tanyin?

589
00:28:42,300 --> 00:28:43,440
What's she been doing these past few days?

590
00:28:43,470 --> 00:28:44,550
Is she still sleeping in her room?

591
00:28:45,060 --> 00:28:46,070
I don't know either.

592
00:28:55,640 --> 00:28:56,430
Ji Tanyin,

593
00:28:57,560 --> 00:28:58,360
