594
00:28:58,390 --> 00:28:59,460
I'm cooking.

595
00:28:59,670 --> 00:29:00,480
Cooking?

596
00:29:01,180 --> 00:29:03,310
I want to make be an automaton that

597
00:29:03,350 --> 00:29:04,790
can both cook and clean.

598
00:29:04,990 --> 00:29:05,790
But,

599
00:29:06,070 --> 00:29:06,950
it seems like

600
00:29:06,950 --> 00:29:07,830
something went wrong,

601
00:29:08,400 --> 00:29:09,430
so it didn't succeed.

602
00:29:12,340 --> 00:29:13,630
You two stop standing here.

603
00:29:13,630 --> 00:29:14,830
Go wait for me over there.

604
00:29:14,830 --> 00:29:15,630
When it's ready,

605
00:29:15,630 --> 00:29:16,740
I'll bring it over to you.

606
00:29:17,550 --> 00:29:18,870
By the way, I've already informed

607
00:29:18,890 --> 00:29:19,890
Xiaoxiang Peak.

608
00:29:19,920 --> 00:29:20,440
From now on,

609
00:29:20,460 --> 00:29:21,980
