your meals from now on.

612
00:29:40,690 --> 00:29:41,500
What's this?

613
00:29:42,110 --> 00:29:43,110
Red Oil Cloud Strings.

614
00:29:43,870 --> 00:29:44,670
And this?

615
00:29:45,150 --> 00:29:46,310
Kidney Bean Immortal Soup.

616
00:29:48,510 --> 00:29:50,590
Then this must be

617
00:29:50,590 --> 00:29:51,590
the Grain Rain Tofu, right?

618
00:29:51,910 --> 00:29:53,860
Yes, you figured it out.

619
00:29:55,790 --> 00:29:56,870
You can't cook,

620
00:29:57,710 --> 00:29:59,190
and your housework is pretty sloppy.

621
00:29:59,260 --> 00:30:00,020
The flowers in the yard died

622
00:30:00,050 --> 00:30:01,330
after you watered them.

623
00:30:01,470 --> 00:30:02,150
I don't think

624
00:30:02,150 --> 00:30:03,500
I've made things hard for you.

625
00:30:04,840 --> 00:30:05,630
So,

626
00:30:05,830 --> 00:30:07,430
why would you overthink things?

627
00:30:07,550 --> 00:30:09,030
Why insist on cooking yourself

628
00:30:09,030 --> 00:30:09,910
and making it difficult for us,

629
00:30:09,910 --> 00:30:11,070
instead of letting Xiaoxiang Peak deliver the food?

630
00:30:11,710 --> 00:30:13,470
Because I want to be your handmaiden.

631
00:30:13,470 --> 00:30:14,310
But you already are

632
00:30:14,310 --> 00:30:15,110
my handmaiden.

633
00:30:15,110 --> 00:30:15,910
It's different.

634
00:30:16,230 --> 00:30:17,020
Before, I only planned

635
00:30:17,020 --> 00:30:18,470
to be your handmaiden for a while.

636
00:30:18,470 --> 00:30:19,190
But now I want

637
00:30:19,190 --> 00:30:20,230
to follow you for a lifetime.

638
00:30:20,230 --> 00:30:21,870
Naturally, I should do my duty well.

639
00:30:27,870 --> 00:30:29,550
Life is long. Don't casually

640
00:30:29,550 --> 00:30:30,710
talk about forever.

641
00:30:30,740 --> 00:30:31,710
I'm different.

642
