667
00:31:18,830 --> 00:31:20,270
My judgment is never wrong.

668
00:31:20,300 --> 00:31:21,110
Good person?

669
00:31:21,310 --> 00:31:22,110
Yes.

670
00:31:32,710 --> 00:31:33,500
High Priest,

671
00:31:33,670 --> 00:31:35,030
since we're talking about this,

672
00:31:35,110 --> 00:31:37,070
let's set some rules.

673
00:31:38,020 --> 00:31:38,830
What rules?

674
00:31:38,830 --> 00:31:39,550
The rules for me being by your side

675
00:31:39,550 --> 00:31:40,710
for a lifetime.

676
00:31:41,070 --> 00:31:43,070
I've sworn to be with you

677
00:31:43,190 --> 00:31:44,640
until you

678
00:31:44,710 --> 00:31:45,700
reach the end of your days.

679
00:31:45,910 --> 00:31:46,670
I promise

680
00:31:46,670 --> 00:31:47,990
to accompany you, take care of you,

681
00:31:47,990 --> 00:31:49,190
and protect you

682
00:31:49,190 --> 00:31:49,830
for the rest of your life,

683
00:31:49,830 --> 00:31:50,710
never interfering with you

684
00:31:50,710 --> 00:31:52,540
or doing anything that might harm you.

685
00:31:52,590 --> 00:31:53,310
Likewise,

686
00:31:53,310 --> 00:31:54,830
you must promise me three things.

687
00:31:55,550 --> 00:31:56,350
First,

688
00:31:56,390 --> 00:31:57,630
you must not leave me.

689
00:31:57,630 --> 00:31:58,510
No matter where you go,

690
00:31:58,510 --> 00:31:59,550
I will follow you closely,

691
00:31:59,550 --> 00:32:00,150
never leaving your side.

692
00:32:00,150 --> 00:32:01,270
No matter what happens to you,

693
00:32:01,270 --> 00:32:02,630
and whatever you go through,

694
00:32:02,630 --> 00:32:03,870
even if the heavens change

695
00:32:03,870 --> 00:32:04,750
and the world collapses,

696
00:32:04,750 --> 00:32:05,950
we must stay together.

697
00:32:06,110 --> 00:32:06,910
Second,

698
00:32:06,950 --> 00:32:07,750
don't ask me too much

699
00:32:07,750 --> 00:32:08,820
about the past.

700
00:32:08,860 --> 00:32:09,790
I won't tell you

701
00:32:09,790 --> 00:32:10,830
everything.

702
00:32:11,020 --> 00:32:12,310
It's for your own good,

703
00:32:12,310 --> 00:32:13,240
because many things

704
00:32:13,240 --> 00:32:14,390
are decided by fate,

705
00:32:14,390 --> 00:32:15,310
and you can't change them,

706
00:32:15,310 --> 00:32:16,470
only accept them.

707
00:32:19,590 --> 00:32:20,360
Third...

708
00:32:23,230 --> 00:32:24,070
What's the third?

709
00:32:24,510 --> 00:32:25,310
Third...

710
00:32:26,670 --> 00:32:27,990
We probably won't reach that point.

711
00:32:28,430 --> 00:32:30,030
Just remember the first two steps.

712
00:32:32,790 --> 00:32:33,750
What are you laughing at?

713
00:32:35,420 --> 00:32:36,240
Nothing.

714
00:32:37,390 --> 00:32:38,190
Do you want to eat?

715
00:32:40,710 --> 00:32:41,590
I'm not very hungry.

716
00:32:41,870 --> 00:32:43,190
If you're not eating, go back and rest.

717
00:32:43,390 --> 00:32:44,510
Do you agree to it?

718
00:32:45,020 --> 00:32:46,110
Go back to sleep.

719
00:32:46,380 --> 00:32:47,180
A good night's sleep

720
00:32:47,210 --> 00:32:48,570
is the first step to welcoming good fortune.

721
00:32:49,000 --> 00:32:50,030
Then I'll go first.

722
00:32:50,510 --> 00:32:51,310
By the way,

723
00:32:51,310 --> 00:32:52,500
if you're really hungry,

724
00:32:52,590 --> 00:32:53,420
just eat a little.

725
00:32:53,420 --> 00:32:54,510
Although it doesn't look good,

726
00:32:54,510 --> 00:32:55,550
it's not poisonous.

727
00:32:55,580 --> 00:32:56,710
As long as it fills you up, it's fine.

728
00:32:56,790 --> 00:32:57,590
Go back.

729
00:32:58,110 --> 00:32:58,910
I'm leaving.

730
00:33:04,910 --> 00:33:06,670
