734
00:34:20,889 --> 00:34:21,679
Guards!

735
00:34:25,110 --> 00:34:25,909
Grand Elder.

736
00:34:30,270 --> 00:34:31,070
With this,

737
00:34:31,510 --> 00:34:33,080
