739
00:34:38,070 --> 00:34:40,190
I'll send someone to deliver the medicine right away.

740
00:34:40,429 --> 00:34:41,230
Okay.

741
00:34:41,590 --> 00:34:43,150
As for Lyu Yao you mentioned,

742
00:34:43,520 --> 00:34:45,080
