746
00:34:55,750 --> 00:34:57,510
This Essence Nourishing Pill is extremely precious.

747
00:34:57,950 --> 00:34:59,140
If it goes missing like this,

748
00:34:59,620 --> 00:35:01,220
even if it's not discovered right away,

749
00:35:01,800 --> 00:35:04,110
it will eventually be noticed.

750
00:35:05,630 --> 00:35:06,430
Young Mistress Dai,

751
00:35:07,040 --> 00:35:09,590
