787
00:36:45,350 --> 00:36:46,470
Don't wander around unnecessarily.

788
00:36:46,670 --> 00:36:47,830
it's better not to let others know,

789
00:36:47,870 --> 00:36:48,910
or it might cause trouble.

790
00:36:52,510 --> 00:36:53,310
You can go now.

